---
title: Quick Black Pepper & Sweet Onion Chicken Stir-Fry with Greens & Rapid Rice
description: Forget takeout: the path to sweet-and-savoury dinner bliss is as simple as breaking out a fry pan. In this easy
recipe, chicken, pepper and onion chutney are coated in tantalizing teriyaki sauce and peanuts are transformed
into the perfect crunchy topping. Everything comes together over a steamy bed of rapid rice. The results? A
symphony of flavours and textures that are so delicious, you might just lick the bowl.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
